 (11/2008)  First paper on bioinformatics : My  first paper  on bioinformatics titled ‚ÄúHuman genomes as email attachments‚Äù has been published on the journal  Bioinformatics . We used novel techniques to compress a human genome from 3.2GB to 4.1MB. From the date we submitted the paper (Oct. 7, 2008) to the date it was published online (Nov. 7, 2008), it took just one month! The PDF is available at  here . It was once the No. 1 most-frequently read article in the Journal of Bioinformatics in January and February of 2009 according to the following  link  (as of March 2009). 
